metadata.name: 001 Hexahedron
metadata.description:
001 Perfect Black Hexahedron

Prismatic Gem that light could pass through
This black cube turned into something that you don't see only one way black

Life isn't dual
There is no black or white good or bad
Every human being could be "good" or "bad" at the same time and they are good and bad at the same time as they are everything between good and bad

Everything in all universes is eternity infinity united 
Everything is one
Without the power of light everything is black
Everything is Perfect Black
